If your `index.php` and `vendor` folder are at the same path, then your `require_once` is wrong. It needs to be:

    require_once __DIR__ . &#39;/vendor/autoload.php&#39;;

`__DIR__` resolves to the directory where the current file is located, so the `vendor` folder is actually located at `__DIR__ . &#39;/vendor/&#39;`.
